wdi2-NE.GDI.STKB.KN.def: Inventories are stocks of goods held by firms to meet temporary or unexpected fluctuations in production or sales, and "work in progress." Data are in constant local currency.
wdi2-NE.GDI.STKB.KN.name: Changes in inventories
wdi2-NE.GDI.STKB.KN.source: World Bank national accounts data, and OECD National Accounts data files.
